He signed to Hospital records in May 2003, and released his first album "Brave Nu World" in 2005.
His second album "Back of Beyond" was released in June 2007.
The third album, Words and Pictures, was released on 28 February 2011 on Hospital Records, and was made available on 2xLP, CD, MP3, and limited edition vinyl.
